{
  "texts": [
    "After doing so, we were left with a 1043-word document, comprised of 45 sentences.",
    "Regarding research question 1, \"To what extent does GPT-4 cite/substantiate claims when writing?\"",
    "we found that 25 out of 45 (55.6%) sentences were unsubstantiated, 17 (37.8%) were substantiated and three (6.7%) were not in need of substantiation (i.e., they were sentences that set up paragraphs).",
    "Ten of the 25 unsubstantiated claims (40%) were due to a lack of citations.",
    "Another 10 (40%) of unsubstantiated sentences contained in-text citations to articles that did not exist."
  ]
}